/*******************************************************************************
*
*       NAME:	scanner.l
*
*   FUNCTION:	Scanner for SMS .r files. 
*
*      USAGE:	
*
*       DATE:	1 June 1994
*
*     AUTHOR:	Tim Turner
*
*	BUGS:	
*
*  REVISIONS:	
*
